     H            Y.
      ** UEXR52 ****************************************************
      *  CHECK DUPLICATE AB#EP70(INVOICE HEADER)                   *
      *  JW     2024.05.06                                         *
      **************************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.
      *                    CALL 'UEXR52 '
      *                    PARM           $NONY   4
      *                    PARM           $DATE   8
      *                    PARM           $RTN    1
      *   IN  $NONY   4A  DELIVERY CODE
      *       $DATE   8A  EFFECTIVE DATE
      *   OUT $RTN    1A  RETURN (Y=EXIST, N=NOT EXIST)
      ***********************************************************
     FAB#EL70 IF  E           K        DISK
      ***********************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $DATE   8
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KNONY   40
     C                     KFLD           KISDT   80
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     KNONY
     C                     MOVEL$DATE     KISDT
      *
     C           KEY1      CHAINAB#EL70              98
      *
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RTN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
